The modules in backend are:

```
src/cli                 CLI scripts
src/api                 FastAPI server
src/loader              Dataset loader and shared model definitions
src/loader/model.py     Pydantic model of dataset types
src/es                  Provide full text search over the dataset, using ElasticSearch
src/duckdb              Provide Relational and Graph DB queries over the dataset, using DuckDB and its DuckPGQ graph database extension
src/duckdb/storage.py   SQL Table and Graph definitions
```

All deps are installed in `venv/` . So when running tests you should use `venv/bin/python -m pytest` or `venv/bin/pytest` to run the tests.